Object.Field:
COMPONENT NAME: RKM DB2 400
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION This KM retrieves: - Physical Files - Database Tables - Database views - Keys - FKs - Check constraints This KM works for DB2/400 database from V4R4 to V5R4.
REQUIREMENTS Required privileges for the connected user: (QSYS and QSYS2 must be accessible)

insert into SNP_REV_TABLE fff ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, RES_NAME, TABLE_ALIAS, TABLE_TYPE, TABLE_DESC_C, IND_SHOW, R_COUNT ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :RES_NAME, :TABLE_ALIAS, :TABLE_TYPE, :TABLE_DESC, '1', :R_COUNT )

select DBXLFI TABLE_NAME, DBXLFI RES_NAME, /* DBXFIL for system name */ case when LOCATE('<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>' ,DBXLFI) <> 0 then SUBSTR( DBXLFI , LOCATE('<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>' ,DBXLFI) + CHAR_LENGTH('<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_ALIAS_LTRIM")%>') ) else SUBSTR(DBXLFI , 1 , 4) end TABLE_ALIAS, case DBXATR when 'PF' then 'T' when 'TB' then 'T' when 'VW' then 'V' end TABLE_TYPE, Trim(IfNull(Trim( Both From DBXTXT ), ' ')||' '||Ifnull(DBXREM, ' ') ) TABLE_DESC, 0 R_COUNT from QSYS.QADBXREF where DBXLIB = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and DBXLFI like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and DBXATR in ('PF' , 'TB' , 'VW')

Insert into SNP_REV_COND ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, COND_NAME, COND_TYPE, COND_SQL, COND_MESS, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :COND_NAME, :COND_TYPE, :COND_SQL, :COND_MESS, '1', '1', '1' )

select t.TABLE_NAME TABLE_NAME, c.CONSTRAINT_NAME COND_NAME, 'D' COND_TYPE, Strip(Substr(c.CHECK_CLAUSE , 1 , 250)) COND_SQL, Strip(c.CONSTRAINT_NAME) || ' Not OK' COND_MESS from QSYS2.SYSCSTDEP t, QSYS2.SYSCHKCST c where t.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and t.CONSTRAINT_NAME = c.CONSTRAINT_NAME and t.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and t.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'

insert into SNP_REV_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, COL_NAME, COL_HEADING, DT_DRIVER, COL_DESC_C, POS, LONGC, SCALEC, COL_MANDATORY, DEF_VALUE, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :COL_NAME, :COL_HEADING, :DT_DRIVER, :COL_DESC, :POS, :LONGC, :SCALEC, :COL_MANDATORY, :DEF_VALUE, '1', '1' )

select DBILFI TABLE_NAME, DBILFL COL_NAME, case Strip(DBITYP) when 'TIMESTMP' then 'TIMESTAMP' else Strip(DBITYP) end DT_DRIVER, Strip(Substr(DBIHDG, 1 , 35)) COL_HEADING, Trim(Ifnull(Trim(Both From DBIHDG),' ')||' '||Ifnull(Trim(Both From DBITXT),' ') ||' '||Ifnull(DBIREM,' ') ) COL_DESC, DBIPOS POS, DBIFLN LONGC, DBINSC SCALEC, case DBINUL when 'Y' then '0' else '1' end COL_MANDATORY, Strip(Substr(DBIDFT , 1 , 100)) DEF_VALUE from QSYS.QADBIFLD where DBILIB = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and DBILFI Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and DBIATR In ('PF' , 'TB' , 'VW')
insert into SNP_REV_KEY_COL ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, COL_NAME, POS ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :COL_NAME, :POS )

select t.DBXLFI TABLE_NAME, k.DBXLFI KEY_NAME, col.DBILFL COL_NAME, c.DBKPOS POS from QSYS.QADBXREF k, QSYS.QADBFDEP r, QSYS.QADBXREF t, QSYS.QADBKFLD c, QSYS.QADBIFLD col where k.DBXFIL = r.DBFFDP and k.DBXLIB = r.DBFLDP and r.DBFFIL = t.DBXFIL and r.DBFLIB = t.DBXLIB and c.DBKLIB = k.DBXLIB and c.DBKFIL = k.DBXFIL and c.Dbklib = col.Dbilib and c.Dbkfil = col.Dbifil and c.Dbkfmt = col.Dbifmt and c.Dbkfld = col.Dbifld and c.DBKFMT = r.DBFRDP and k.DBXUNQ In ('U' , 'V') and t.DBXLIB = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and t.DBXLFI Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' Union All select k.TABLE_NAME TABLE_NAME, k.CONSTRAINT_NAME KEY_NAME, c.COLUMN_NAME COL_NAME, c.ORDINAL_POSITION POS from QSYS2.SYSCST k , QSYS2.SYSKEYCST c where k.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and k.CONSTRAINT_NAME = c.CONSTRAINT_NAME and k.TABLE_SCHEMA = c.TABLE_SCHEMA and k.TABLE_NAME = c.TABLE_NAME and k.CONSTRAINT_TYPE = 'PRIMARY KEY' and k.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and k.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'

insert into SNP_REV_JOIN ( MOD_GUID, FK_NAME, TABLE_NAME, FK_TYPE, PK_SCHEMA, PK_TABLE_NAME, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW, IND_ACTIVE ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :FK_NAME, :FK_TABLE_NAME, 'D' , :SCHEMA_NAME, :PK_TABLE_NAME, '1', '1', '1' )

select c.CONSTRAINT_NAME FK_NAME, c.TABLE_NAME FK_TABLE_NAME, p.TABLE_SCHEMA SCHEMA_NAME, p.TABLE_NAME PK_TABLE_NAME from QSYS2.SYSCSTDEP c, QSYS2.SYSREFCST r, QSYS2.SYSCST p where c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = r.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and c.CONSTRAINT_NAME = r.CONSTRAINT_NAME and r.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = p.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and r.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_NAME = p.CONSTRAINT_NAME and c.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and c.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and p.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and p.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'

insert into SNP_REV_JOIN_COL ( MOD_GUID, FK_NAME, FK_COL_NAME, FK_TABLE_NAME, PK_COL_NAME, PK_TABLE_NAME, POS ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :FK_NAME, :FK_COL_NAME, :FK_TABLE_NAME, :PK_COL_NAME, :PK_TABLE_NAME, :POS )

select c.TABLE_NAME FK_TABLE_NAME, p.TABLE_NAME PK_TABLE_NAME, c.CONSTRAINT_NAME FK_NAME, c.COLUMN_NAME FK_COL_NAME, p.COLUMN_NAME PK_COL_NAME, c.ORDINAL_POSITION POS from QSYS2.SYSKEYCST c, QSYS2.SYSREFCST r, QSYS2.SYSKEYCST p where c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = r.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and c.CONSTRAINT_NAME = r.CONSTRAINT_NAME and r.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = p.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and r.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_NAME = p.CONSTRAINT_NAME and c.ORDINAL_POSITION = p.ORDINAL_POSITION and c.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and c.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and p.TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and p.TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'

insert into SNP_REV_KEY ( MOD_GUID, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, CONS_TYPE, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_FLOW, CHECK_STAT ) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :CONS_TYPE, '1', '1', '1' )

select t.DBXLFI TABLE_NAME, k.DBXLFI KEY_NAME, 'AK' CONS_TYPE from QSYS.QADBXREF k, QSYS.QADBFDEP r, QSYS.QADBXREF t where k.DBXFIL = r.DBFFDP and k.DBXLIB = r.DBFLDP and r.DBFFIL = t.DBXFIL and r.DBFLIB = t.DBXLIB and k.DBXUNQ In ('U' , 'V') and t.DBXLIB = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and t.DBXLFI like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' union all select TABLE_NAME TABLE_NAME, CONSTRAINT_NAME KEY_NAME, 'PK' CONS_TYPE from QSYS2.SYSCST where CONSTRAINT_TYPE = 'PRIMARY KEY' and TABLE_SCHEMA = '<%=odiRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and TABLE_NAME Like '<%=odiRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'
